-- China Must Strengthen Supervision of Derivatives, CSRC's Song Anping Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-25T11:55:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/china-must-strengthen-supervision-of-derivatives-csrc-s-song-anping-says.html

          
          
             China must strengthen its
supervision of derivatives as the global financial crisis was a
“warning bell” on the use of these financial instruments, Song
Anping, Deputy Director-General of the China Securities
Regulatory Commission’s Department of Futures Supervision, said
at a financial forum in Shanghai.  
